qMetaDef.title: Days Since Last Reload
qMetaDef.description: How many days since the last reload of this app?

qStringExpression.qExpr: 'The count of distinct applications.'

qMeasure.qLabel: Apps Over CPU Reload Time Threshold

qStringExpression.qExpr: 'Count of apps which exceeded the specified CPU reload time threshold of ' & If(GetPossibleCount(ReloadCPUTimeThreshold)<>1,'<Varies Across Tenants>',Num(ReloadCPUTimeThreshold,'#,##0')) & ' milliseconds.'

qMetaDef.title: Apps Over CPU Reload Time Threshold

qStringExpression.qExpr: 'If an application has a cpu reload time of greater than ' & If(GetPossibleCount(ReloadCPUTimeThreshold)<>1,'<Varies Across Tenants>',Num(ReloadCPUTimeThreshold,'#,##0')) & ' ms.'
'If the number of distinct fields within an application is over a thresholds, currently set at ' & If(GetPossibleCount(NoOfFields)<>1,'<Varies Across Tenants>',NoOfFields) & ' fields.'

'If the field cardinality of a field is over the set threshold, currently set at ' & If(GetPossibleCount(FieldCardinalityThreshold)<>1,'<Varies Across Tenants>',Num(FieldCardinalityThreshold,'#,##0')) & '.'

'Indicates if the number of values within a given field (in a given table within an app) exceeds the currently set threshold of ' & If(GetPossibleCount(FieldValueCountThreshold)<>1,'<Varies Across Tenants>',Num(FieldValueCountThreshold,'#,##0'))

'If a table exceeds the threshold for number of records in a table, currently set to ' & If(GetPossibleCount(TableRecordCountThreshold)<>1,'<Varies Across Tenants>',Num(TableRecordCountThreshold,'#,##0')) & '.'

'If a table exceeds the threshold for number of records in a table, currently set to ' & If(GetPossibleCount(TableRecordCountThreshold)<>1,'<Varies Across Tenants>',Num(TableRecordCountThreshold,'#,##0')) & '.'
'If a table has greater than ' & If(GetPossibleCount(TableRecordCountThreshold)<>1,'<Varies Across Tenants>',Num(TableRecordCountThreshold,'#,##0')) & ' records, the current set threshold.'

'The percentage of the base RAM footprint per-app against the tenant quota, which is ' & If(GetPossibleCount(AppRAMSizeQuota)=1,If(IsNum(AppRAMSizeQuota),AppRAMSizeQuota/1024/1024 & ' MB.',AppRAMSizeQuota),'<Varies Across Tenants>')

qMetaDef.title: Avg App RAM Footprint (GB)
qMetaDef.description:
(Average) The memory footprint of an app when reloaded. 
Note that in practice, this is the baseline memory consumed by an app. As users make selections and navigate the app, additional memory will be cached by the app.

qMetaDef.title: Table # of Fields
qMetaDef.description: Count of fields per table.

qMeasure.qLabel: App Reload Peak RAM Against Quota

qMetaDef.title: App Reload Peak RAM Against Quota
qMetaDef.description: The peak RAM used in an application's reload against the set quota, which is 5 GB.

qMetaDef.title: # Tables
qMetaDef.description: Count of unique tables within apps.

qMetaDef.title: # Fields
qMetaDef.description: Count of unique fields within apps.

qStringExpression.qExpr: 'The count of managed spaces within a tenant'
'(Average) The average rolling base RAM footprint. The current rolling window is set to ' & $(vu_track_app_meta_retention) & ' days.'

'If the app has a base RAM footprint is over ' & ($(vAppRAMToQuotaPercentThreshold)*100) & '% of the tenant per-app RAM quota, where the quota is ' 
& If(Only({<QuotaResource={'app_mem_size'}>} Quota_MB) <> 'Unlimited',Num(Avg({<QuotaResource={'app_mem_size'}>} Quota_MB),'#,##0'), Num(Only(Quota_MB),'#,##0')) & ' MB.'

qMetaDef.title: Synthetic Fields
qMetaDef.description: Fields which are common across more than one table, thus creating a synthetic key.

qMetaDef.title: App Reload Peak RAM (MB)
qMetaDef.description: The peak memory that an application consumes on reload, which can be significantly higher than the base RAM footprint due to temp RAM utilized for additional calculations, aggregations, memory intensive functions (think rand()), etc.

qStringExpression.qExpr: 'Count of records within a field in a table in an app. Note that synthetic key fields will report # Field Records = 0. Please use Field Cardinality for these fields.'

qMetaDef.title: Field RAM Footprint (MB)
qMetaDef.description:
Initial memory consumed by a field within an during reload.
In aggregate, this total Field RAM footprint might be larger than the total App RAM footprint due to fields existing on more than one table.
(Measure shading / coloring relative to the max value found for this measure in your current selections.)

qStringExpression.qExpr:
'If using Qlik Sense Business, there is a quota on the number of shared spaces, which is ' 
& If(Only({<QuotaResource={'shared_spaces'}>}QuotaSpace)<>'Unlimited',Avg({<QuotaResource={'shared_spaces'}>}QuotaSpace),Only(QuotaSpace)) & '.'

qMetaDef.title: Apps Contain Data Island(s)
qMetaDef.description:
Count of apps which contain one or more island tables in the data model.
An island table is one which does not share any common field with another table and, therefore, is not associated with other data tables.

qStringExpression.qExpr:
'The tenant quota for the base RAM footprint of an application, which is ' 
& If(Only({<QuotaResource={'app_mem_size'}>} Quota_MB) <> 'Unlimited',Num(Avg({<QuotaResource={'app_mem_size'}>} Quota_MB),'#,##0'), Num(Only(Quota_MB),'#,##0')) & ' MB.'

qMetaDef.title: Total Table RAM Footprint (MB)
qMetaDef.description:
Net impact to RAM for a table in an app.
(Measure shading / coloring relative to the max value found for this measure in your current selections.)

qStringExpression.qExpr: 'If using Qlik Sense Business, there is a quota on the number of shared spaces within a tenant. This measure reports the percentage of that quota.'

qMetaDef.title: App RAM Footprint (MB)
qMetaDef.description:
The memory footprint of an app when reloaded. 
Note that in practice, this is the baseline memory consumed by an app. As users make selections and navigate the app, additional memory will be cached by the app.

qMetaDef.title: Table RAM Footprint (MB)
qMetaDef.description: The memory footprint of a data table within an app when reloaded.

qMetaDef.title: Avg App RAM Footprint (MB)
qMetaDef.description:
(Average) The memory footprint of an app when reloaded. 
Note that in practice, this is the baseline memory consumed by an app. As users make selections and navigate the app, additional memory will be cached by the app.

qStringExpression.qExpr: 'The count of shared spaces.'

qMetaDef.title: App RAM Footprint (GB)
qMetaDef.description:
The memory footprint of an app when reloaded. 
Note that in practice, this is the baseline memory consumed by an app. As users make selections and navigate the app, additional memory will be cached by the app.

qMetaDef.title: App Contains Synthetic Keys
qMetaDef.description:
Indicates if an app's data model contains one or more synthetic keys.
A synthetic key is created when two or more fields are found in two or more tables within an app data model.

qMetaDef.title: Field Cardinality
qMetaDef.description: Cardinality is a measure of uniqueness of field values. Higher cardinality means more unique field values, which generally results in higher memory utilization.

qStringExpression.qExpr: 'The quota for the maximum app upload size, which is ' & If(Only({<QuotaResource={'app_upload_disk_size'}>} Quota_MB) <> 'Unlimited',Avg({<QuotaResource={'app_upload_disk_size'}>} Quota_MB), Only(Quota_MB)) & ' MB.'

qMetaDef.title: Table # Records
qMetaDef.description: Count of records within a given table in an app data model.

qMetaDef.title: App Contains Circular Reference(s)
qMetaDef.description: The number of apps that contain circular references (loops) in their data models.

qMetaDef.title: Last Reload Time
qMetaDef.description: The latest timestamp when an app was reloaded in Sense.

qStringExpression.qExpr: ''(Average) The average rolling base RAM footprint. The current rolling window is set to ' & $(vu_track_app_meta_retention) & ' days.'

qMetaDef.title: App Contains Data Island(s)
qMetaDef.description: The number of apps that contain data islands (tables that are not associated to any other tables within the data model).

qMetaDef.title: Island Tables
qMetaDef.description: Count of tables within an app which are "islands", meaning that they are not associated with any other table in the data model.

qMetaDef.title: Reload CPU Time
qMetaDef.description: Engine CPU time spent during last app reload, given in milliseconds (ms). Note: this is not the same as Reload Duration reported in other Monitor Apps, but is specific to the time that the engine spent to reload the app.
